===Etymology===
For the "firewood" and "torch" senses, from {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*təŋ|t=pine; fir}}; compare {{cog|my|ထင်း|t=firewood}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

For the "evaporate, steam" senses, see {{och-l|烝|}} for more.

